pageTitle: Itinerary for Wednesday, November 23, 2016 | Prime Minister of Canada
articleHtml:
Itinerary for the Prime Minister, Justin Trudeau, for Wednesday, November 23, 2016:

Ottawa, Ontario

10:00 a.m. The Prime Minister will attend the National Caucus meeting.

4:00 p.m. The Prime Minister will depart for Monrovia, Liberia.

Canada Reception Centre
Hangar 11
190 Convair Private,
Ottawa, Ontario

Notes for media:

  • Photo opportunity only
  • Media should arrive no later than 3:00 p.m.

PMO Media Relations: 
Media@pmo-cpm.gc.ca
613-957-5555
